    <div class="relative pt-36 ml-auto">
      <div class="lg:w-2/3 text-center mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-white font-bold text-5xl md:text-6xl xl:text-7xl">
          Roambank
        </h1>
        <h2 class="text-slate-100 font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl xl:text-4xl">
          Driving a Greener Tomorrow
        </h2>
        
        <p class="mt-8 text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-300">
          Roambank is a digital platform designed to revolutionize door-to-door
          trash collection through the use of IoT-based weighing systems,
          real-time data, and hyperlocal routing. By offering accurate and
          transparent measurement of collected waste, Roambank ensures fair
          compensation for 'rombeng' (waste collectors), and provides direct
          feedback on the value of the materials collected. The platform
          utilizes geofencing and routing technologies to optimize waste
          collectors' routes, reducing operational costs and improving service
          efficiency.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          Roambank directly connects waste collectors with local recycling banks
          and SMEs focused on recycling, fostering business-to-business (B2B)
          relationships that strengthen the circular economy. This integration
          enables small businesses to access valuable raw materials, boosting
          local entrepreneurship and economic growth.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          Roambankâ€™s competitive edge lies in its hyperlocal approach, which
          allows for highly tailored operations within specific areas.
        </p>

